Financial services


Founded
1988; 29 years ago (1988)
Richmond, Virginia, U.S.[1]


Founder
Richard Fairbank, Nigel Morris


Headquarters
McLean, Virginia[2]



Key people


Richard Fairbank
(Chairman, President and CEO)
Stephen S. Crawford
(Head of Finance and Corporate Development)[3]
